  <description>
    <p>The coolest winter sport has finally come to your Linux machine!
    </p>
    <p>
      Win the Championship and unlock all the 100+ real-world teams of the following leagues
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>North American Broomball League</li>
      <li>Maritime Broomball Association</li>
      <li>Penrith Broomball competition</li>
      <li>Ontario League</li>
      <li>Italian Broomball League</li>
      <li>Swiss Broomball Association A + B</li>
      <li>International Women League</li>
      <li>International League</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Main features</p>
    <ul>
      <li>100+ real-world teams</li>
      <li>20+ different styled balls to collect</li>
      <li>Privacy friendly</li>
      <li>Offline game</li>
      <li>Created with Godot Engine 3</li>
    </ul>
    <p>PS: If you want to add a broomball team to the game, send me a mail at info@simondalvai.org</p>
  </description>
